      "name": "技能",
      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "talent",
          "data": {
            "list": [
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">普通攻击</span></p><p>造成2点<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">物理伤害</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/06/14/157749474/10316b5178d5109d597f415d6e7903dc_6345784930604791099.png",
                "key": "旋规设矩",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "dendro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "black"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "旋规设矩"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">元素战技</span></p><p>造成2点<span style=\"color: #99FF88\">草元素伤害</span>，生成<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">迸发扫描</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/06/14/157749474/5939d61b0bbbc9069caa164fbf967189_1973394462529406308.png",
                "key": "画则巧施",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "dendro"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "画则巧施"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">元素爆发</span></p><p>造成3点<span style=\"color: #99FF88\">草元素伤害</span>，本角色附属<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">梅赫拉克的助力</span>，生成2层<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">迸发扫描</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/06/14/157749474/23c5b1ed3865c0fe1cc2409747bb043a_6200817550508966312.png",
                "key": "繁绘隅穹",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "dendro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "繁绘隅穹"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span>附着草元素，可发生元素反应：</span></p><p><span>【</span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">草元素</span><span>+</span><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span><span>】</span><span style=\"color: white\">绽放</span>：本伤害<span>+1，生成使下次火/雷伤害+2的[</span><span style=\"color: white\">草原核</span><span>]</span></p><p><span>【</span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">草元素</span><span>+</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span><span>】</span><span style=\"color: white\">燃烧</span>：本伤害<span>+1，生成回合结束时造成1点火伤害的[</span><span style=\"color: white\">燃烧烈焰</span><span>]（可用次数1，最多叠加到2）</span></p><p><span>【</span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">草元素</span><span>+</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span><span>】</span><span style=\"color: white\">原激化</span>：本伤害<span>+1，生成使下3次草/雷伤害+1的[</span><span style=\"color: white\">激化领域</span><span>]</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/06/14/157749474/e8cff941b5a0ff248efde360ec9e91fe_8317060822335862520.png",
                "key": "草元素伤害",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "草元素伤害"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">物理伤害</span></strong></p><p>物理伤害不会附着元素，也不会发生元素反应。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">迸发扫描</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">出战状态</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">双方选择行动前：</span>如果我方场上存在草原核或丰穰之核，则使其<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次数</span>-1，并<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">舍弃</span>我方牌库顶的1张卡牌。然后，造成所<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">舍弃</span>卡牌原本元素骰费用+1的<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">草元素伤害</span>。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次数：1</span>（可叠加，最多叠加到3次）</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次数</span></strong></p><p>此牌效果触发后，会消耗1次<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次数</span>；</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次数</span>耗尽后，立刻弃置此牌。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">舍弃</span></strong></p><p>通过行动牌或角色技能的效果，将行动牌从手牌或牌库中弃置。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">梅赫拉克的助力</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">状态</span></p><p>角色「普通攻击」造成的伤害+1，且造成的<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">物理伤害</span>变为<span style=\"color: #99FF88\">草元素伤害</span>。</p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">角色普通攻击后：</span>生成<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">迸发扫描</span>。</p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">持续回合：2</span></p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">持续回合</span></strong></p><p>每回合结束阶段，<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">持续回合</span>-1；</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">持续回合</span>耗尽后，立刻弃置此牌。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/06/14/157749474/07bae546ac7c69ef6402170b283840c5_8239549135247375364.png",
